        <h2 class="left-heading destination-section-heading">Airport Mesa Vortex</h2>
        <p>Around the city there are several spots that are said to be energy vortexes which also offer stunning views, the most popular being the <strong>Airport Mesa Vortex</strong>. This vortex which sits atop a rocky mesa hill near the airport and offers breathtaking panoramic views over Southern Sedona and many surrounding natural features. The vortex is accessible via a very short hike from the parking area.</p>
        <p>Also near the airport is the <strong>Sedona Airport Overlook</strong>, which looks out over Western Sedona with towering gorgeous red rock cliffs and mountains behind the city.</p>
    </section>



